                    },
                    "locales": {
                        "en": {
                            "text": "<p>This website is becoming a {{personal blog}} instead of a technical showcase.</p><p>I want it to be a place for diaries, self-introspection, life notes, and the small observations that are easy to lose when everything is only stored in chats, tasks, or code.</p><p>The technical material still exists, but this public space is now more about [[remembering how life feels while I am learning and changing]].</p>"
                        },
                        "zh": {
                            "text": "<p>这个网站正在从技术展示页变成一个{{个人博客}}。</p><p>我想把它当作日记、自我反思、生活记录，以及一些容易被聊天、任务和代码淹没的小观察的存放处。</p><p>技术内容仍然保留着，但这个公开空间现在更想记录[[我在学习和变化时，生活本身是什么感觉]]。</p>"
                        }
                    }
                }
